Title="Tau ´Ri - City of Steel"

[SpecialEvent0]
Message="Warning message!"

[SpecialEvent1]
Message="An enemy has entered our city."

[SpecialEvent2]
Message="He is armed and extremely dangerous..."

[SpecialEvent3]
Message="Therefore a strict curfew now applies to section 16."

[SpecialEvent4]
Message="Thought Police: Drop your weapons and surrender immediately."

[SpecialEvent5]
Message="Thought Police: You have 10 seconds, then we open fire."

[SpecialEvent6]
Message="Thought Police: FIRE!"

[TranslatorEvent0]
Message="My Log: I must hurry. Shortly the Thought Police will arrive here in large numbers. The sewer and ventilation systems are not safe. Soon they will start scanning."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent1]
Message="My Log: Closed. For now even the best will not be able to pass through the door."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent2]
Message="My Log: What a tremendous void, it's so far to the bottom of this shaft."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent3]
Message="My Log: This passageway appears to be suitable for use."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent4]
Message="My Log: So finally I'm in the town and somewhat safer, especially in this intricate system of halls. Looking at the posters of big brother makes the people feel, they are being monitored."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent5]
Message="My Log: The apartments are modestly furnished. Old rickety bunks and a small table with chairs. They have just one room. Some also have a small kitchenette for the convenience of residents."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent6]
Message="My Log: The corridors are dimly lit. Is no one doing maintenance? Some are lit and some not."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent7]
Message="My Log: This door is locked. It makes no sense to go through all the apartments, I'll just run into someone. Violence between people is very common, so it is better to be quiet."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent8]
Message="My Log: No sense trying the lift. Even at the best times, it seldom worked, and presently the electricity is cut off during the day, as part of austerity measures."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent9]
Message="My Log: This place looks familiar. If I'm not mistaken, my apartment is just two floors up."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent10]
Message="My Log: This screen both sends and receives. Every sound is captured. They can see me too. One is never sure at any moment, if the Thought Police is watching. It's assumed to be constant. They can turn it on, if they want to."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent11]
Message="My Log: For some reason, the screen is placed in an unusual position. Normally, it's on the front wall, where it scans the whole room towards the window. This niche with the bookshelf lies outside the view of the screen."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent12]
Message="My Log: It's better to turn the back on them while they watch. But even a back can reveal secret thoughts."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent13]
Message="My Log: So I'm finally home after so much time and I still will not have peace."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent14]
Message="My Log: There are rumors, some sort of brotherhood is fighting against the government. The problem is to find the way to them. They are our only hope. Great, the Thought Police will be here in no time now."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent15]
Message="My Log: Kramek's consumer goods. As usual, the shelves are almost empty. Even shoelaces and razor blades are impossible to get for months now."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent16]
Message="My Log: What's this? A secret room or passage? In this huge city, many people could use such secrets."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent17]
Message="My Log: Store's secret sale place. Wow, CDs with metal music and pictures. If the Thought Police knew... This is only for a few customers. Getting CDs is impossible now. I am amazed that these were made when the material was hard to get."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent18]
Message="My Log: Cinemas play the same war movies like a refugee ship being bombed. The audience loved when humans fled a helicopter chasing them. It was seen through a gun sight. People were shot bloody, then they died. The audience roared with laughter."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent19]
Message="My Log: Then there was a lifeboat full of children and above it a helicopter. It dropped a bomb. Terrific flash, boat exploded to splinters and a child's hand flew high in the air. There were huge applauses from the Party members."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent20]
Message="My Log: Stairs to other floors collapsed long ago due to insufficient maintenance. The stairs in the hotel are required so they are kept in good condition."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent21]
Message="My Log: Standard toilets. No one has a privacy partition, because it's a ''luxury''. Small video screens are also on the toilet."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent22]
Message="My Log: This looks like a good escape. The sewers spread all over, even when the main gate is closed."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent23]
Message="My Log: In the cellars screens are in the hallways and in some rooms. Mostly there are only microphones. So if you are quiet, you can do what you want."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent24]
Message="My Log: Local cafe. People come here to play chess or just chat over a glass of gin."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent25]
Message="My Log: Hotel room with a modified screen? The unit has a tape that plays over and over again. So they still see an empty room. I've heard about this, it's a secret entrance to the old section."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent27]
Message="My Log: A sensor automatically closes this. Even if someone finds the false door in the closet, they only see a wall."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent28]
Message="My Log: This cable shaft could get me into the old section."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"

[TranslatorEvent29]
Message="My Log: We formed a resistance gang and finally managed to get a gun and a decoder. Now we can break the security codes for doors. There's a secret closet in an hotel room. It's a great shortcut to the old section and the ''Brotherhood''."
M_NewMessage="My Log"
M_TransMessage="My Log"
